FAST FORWARD 7 YEARS OF FUCKSTICKS

&nbsp;

When he was little his dad stored some oil or some shit beneath the yard, and capped it with a pipe to the surface level to let in regularly circulated air.  One day he saw it dripping black like blood into a puddle of oil in the dirt. He wondered what it tasted like. Evil has followed him around ever since… just for shits and giggles.

&nbsp;

She was in a similar way. He remembers the first time he saw her. He was climbing up dark stairs to his bedroom. The hall at the top was pitch black. And all he could see was her perfect face atop a yellow puffy coat. “Another one bites the dust” ran through his head. It reminded him of her. Climbing the stairs in her yellow puffy coat, on her hands and knees, with her tongue hanging out of her mouth in a sexy way. It was the first time he ever thought of girls that way.

&nbsp;

Immediately after she was swept away to the mutilation factory section of the joy division, where german doctors did empirical research on threshold of pain. Taking off limbs without pain killers, for example. Not because the subjects needed to be amputated, but the doctors needed to research how bad the human would scream before all limbs were gone.

&nbsp;

She didn’t flinch an inch. She was a waterfall. The pain flowed down to a clear puddle of blood, or should I say tears, or should I say angel tears.  There was nothing wrong with her. Whatsmore, she didn’t feel a fucking thing, and thanks to him, Core, she, LG, was whole again by morning.

&nbsp;

Core worked with creation and damnation. Each sat atop his shoulders like an orb, one black and one white, and he just walked around and observed, and looked for her; her color was red (go figure).

&nbsp;

In Spokane he’d brought the end of the world through the pain of tears, just looking for her and dealing with fucksticks in the way: black witches, white witches, vampires (actually quite helpful), aliens (also quite helpful), devil dogs, greed demons, redneck zombies (note: cubes of ice in beauty bark works well), etcetera.

&nbsp;

Then the orbs said, “sooo how do you like the silence?  Are you enjoying the silence?”  Yellow street lights (all of them were yellow, like LG’s puffy coat) blinked to no one.  It was eerie as fuck being the only person on the planet. Thank God (aka white orb) he was wearing contacts, so he wouldn’t be THAT GUY on the twilight zone.

&nbsp;

So whitey orb and blackey orb put shit back together for little old Core, and started the clock on the next epoch; the next cylinder of space time; time for another round of reminding him of who he was, and finding her.

&nbsp;

It was literally, not figuratively, a pain in the neck.  Every time some fuckstick decided to hack her in the neck with an axe, she just  walked away like nothing happened, but his neck got really fucking sore.

&nbsp;

Fast forward 7 years: He was sick of it. He was going to do something about it. Despite his feat of saving these pricks in the first place, THEY went on like nothing happened.  Fuck them.  7 fucking years ain’t long enough to forget, those fucksticks.

